[Encouraging people to vaccinate is wise, as in the south our warm weather continues a bit longer than other areas. The WNV vaccine is usually in combination with the Eastern and Western equine encephalitis vaccines.

Why the increase? Perhaps it is only due to reporting?

Oklahoma may be found on the interactive healthmap at: http://healthmap.org/r/3Z3N
- Mod.TG]
